<COREF ID="29" TYPE="IDENT">Huang Chun - ming 's</COREF> use of fiction to express <COREF ID="29" TYPE="IDENT">his</COREF> concern for the elderly has a long history .
" Cheng - tsai Gets off the Bus , " <COREF ID="29" TYPE="IDENT">Huang 's</COREF> earliest published work , is the tale of <COREF ID="41" TYPE="IDENT">an elderly woman</COREF> taking <COREF ID="41" TYPE="IDENT">her</COREF> grandson to the city to visit <COREF ID="41" TYPE="IDENT">her</COREF> daughter and son - in - law .
