What really marks <COREF ID="41" TYPE="IDENT">her</COREF> as elderly is not <COREF ID="41" TYPE="IDENT">her</COREF> visage , however , but <COREF ID="41" TYPE="IDENT">her</COREF> inability to carry out a task as simple as catching a bus into the city , and the apprehensive feelings <COREF ID="41" TYPE="IDENT">she</COREF> harbors towards the " cold , unfamiliar " city and the unknown future .
