Old people " let go " by the modern era
This theme of tragedy resulting from changing times has appeared in <COREF ID="12" TYPE="IDENT">Huang 's</COREF> earlier work , in " <COREF ID="21" TYPE="IDENT">Cymbal</COREF> , " for example , which was strongly influenced by Lu Xun 's The Story of Ah Q .
