<COREF ID="6" TYPE="IDENT">Chin 's</COREF> work - making announcements in the street while using a cymbal to attract attention - has been made obsolete by the spread of the megaphone , undercutting <COREF ID="6" TYPE="IDENT">his</COREF> social status and taking away <COREF ID="6" TYPE="IDENT">his</COREF> livelihood .
