<COREF ID="34" TYPE="IDENT">Their</COREF> tragedy is that <COREF ID="34" TYPE="IDENT">they</COREF> are out of step with the times , that <COREF ID="34" TYPE="IDENT">they</COREF> do not know how to adapt to this cold and chaotic new society .
