<COREF ID="34" TYPE="IDENT">Their</COREF> guesses are all wrong , of course , but in <COREF ID="34" TYPE="IDENT">their</COREF> creation of misunderstanding upon misunderstanding , we see a different kind of dignity .
And in <COREF ID="14" TYPE="IDENT">this " old " wisdom and these " old " ways</COREF> , we also see a light that time can not dim .
